title: Adshares (ADS) Syrup Pool.
body:
We would like to propose creating Adshares (ADS) Syrup Pool. Project from 2017 with live product has becomes cross-chain on 12.05.2021. Adshares team plan to allocate ADS Staking from token release for Pancake Swap asap.
